ActPublic Service Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Film Board - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the National Film Board ENTER INTO A COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada, in respect of its employees in the Administrative and Foreign Service category and the Scientific and Professional category, which agreement is from July 1, 2018 to June 30, 2022.
